code: protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     SplunkConfiguration configuration = splunkConfigurationFactory.parseMap(parameters).     configuration.setName(remaining).     setProperties(configuration, parameters).     return new SplunkEndpoint(uri, this, configuration). }

/**  * To use the {@link SplunkConfigurationFactory}  */ public void setSplunkConfigurationFactory(SplunkConfigurationFactory splunkConfigurationFactory) {     this.splunkConfigurationFactory = splunkConfigurationFactory. }
